hanisms. Performing such a\ntest on other classes of SNe (e.g., superluminous SNe) can be used to rule out\nthe interaction model for a class of events.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Apr 2014 21:26:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
